for setting up equations, follow:

http://stackoverflow.com/questions/10987992/using-mathjax-with-jekyll

at a console:

gem install kramdown

add in _config.yml:
markdown: kramdown

add the line:

<script type="text/javascript" src="http://cdn.mathjax.org/mathjax/latest/MathJax.js?config=TeX-AMS-MML_HTMLorMML"></script>
 
after <title> line in your _layouts/default.html

to changel font size, change style.css in root directory

to change equation size, change _layout/default.html Mathjax setup script 
